<section id="sponsors" class="py-24 px-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-4 block font-sans text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.3] tracking-normal text-blue-gray-900 antialiased">
      Sponsors
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-8 block text-left text-lg text-gray-600">
      The success of the Digital Library Federation's Annual Forum is made possible through the generous support of our sponsors, whose contributions are vital to creating an enriching and impactful experience for all attendees. These organizations share our commitment to advancing innovation, collaboration, and knowledge-sharing within the digital library community. Their support enables us to offer a dynamic program featuring presentations, workshops, and networking opportunities that drive the field forward. By partnering with us, our sponsors demonstrate their dedication to fostering a vibrant community of practice. We are deeply grateful for their investment in the Forum, which helps ensure its accessibility, quality, and long-term sustainability. Together, we are shaping the future of digital libraries and empowering the professionals who make this work possible!
    </p>
    <p class="mt-20">
      <a href="/prospectus/" class="align-middle select-none font-sans font-bold text-center uppercase transition-all disabled:opacity-50 disabled:shadow-none disabled:pointer-events-none text-sm py-3.5 px-7 rounded-lg bg-blue-800 text-white shadow-md shadow-blue-800/10 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-800/20 focus:opacity-[0.85] focus:shadow-none active:opacity-[0.85] active:shadow-none bg-blue-800" type="button" data-ripple-light="true">
        Sponsor DLF Forum
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="px-6 py-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Thank You to Our Sponsors</h1>
  <p class="text-center text-lg mb-12">
    We are deeply grateful to our sponsors for their generous support of the DLF Forum.
  </p>

  {% for group in sponsorsByLevel %}
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-800">{{ group.level }} Sponsors</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
        {% if group.sponsors.length %}
          {% for sponsor in group.sponsors %}
            <a href="{{ sponsor.url }}" target="_blank" aria-label="Read more about {{ sponsor.name }}" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex justify-center">
              {% if sponsor.isSvg %}
                <div class="{% if group.level == 'Platinum' %}w-72{% else %}w-52{% endif %} h-auto [&>svg]:w-full [&>svg]:h-auto [&>svg]:object-contain">
                  {{ sponsor.svg | safe }}
                </div>
              {% else %}
                <img src="{{ sponsor.logo }}" alt="{{ sponsor.name }}" class="{% if group.level == 'Platinum' %}w-72{% else %}w-52{% endif %} h-auto object-contain"/>
              {% endif %}
            </a>
          {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
          <p class="text-center text-gray-700 col-span-full">
            <a href="/prospectus/" class="align-middle select-none font-sans font-bold text-center uppercase transition-all disabled:opacity-50 disabled:shadow-none disabled:pointer-events-none text-sm py-3.5 px-7 rounded-lg bg-blue-800 text-white shadow-md shadow-blue-800/10 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-800/20 focus:opacity-[0.85] focus:shadow-none active:opacity-[0.85] active:shadow-none bg-blue-800" type="button" data-ripple-light="true">
              Sponsor DLF Forum
            </a>
          </p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

